&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the quarterly and annual income tax provision process, including review of calculations prepared by external tax service providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review technical analyses related to uncertain tax positions, valuation allowances, and tax implications of complex transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate and timely tax disclosures for SEC filings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain documentation and internal controls supporting the tax provision process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Risk Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee global income tax compliance prepared by external service providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage external tax advisors to ensure high-quality, cost-effective support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain tax-related internal controls in compliance with SOX requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor changes in tax laws and assess Company impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration Accounting Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support accounting for collaboration and licensing arrangements, including the initial operationalization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with revenue recognition, cost-sharing, and milestone accounting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tax Operations &amp;amp; Advisory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the Company’s internal lead for tax matters coordinating external consultants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance to internal stakeholders leveraging external advisors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
