&lt;li&gt;As a member of the CMC project teams, provide strategic CMC regulatory leadership to develop and execute sound regulatory strategies that meet global regulatory requirements and enable Vir business objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide CMC regulatory expertise to enable global development and registration for INDs, CTAs, BLAs and MAAs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and communicate regulatory risks and facilitate the development and execution of risk mitigation strategies in concert with Technical Operation functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan strategy for and lead HA interactions for CMC specific issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage CMC regulatory changes throughout the product life cycle, including support for relevant quality systems related to change control, discrepancy management, as well as Health Authority inspection support (as applicable)&lt;/li&gt;
